                    | Bronze layer           | Silver layer                | Gold layer                  |
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Definition          |      Raw unprocessed   |                             |   
                    | data from data sources | Clean and standardized data | Business ready data         | 
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Objective           | Traceability           |                             | Provide data to be consumed 
                    | and debugging          | Prepare data for analysis   | for reporting and analytics | 
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Object type         | Tables                 | Tables                      | Views                       | 
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Load method         | Full load              | Full load                   | None                        | 
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Data transformation | Unmodified             | Cleaning,                   | Integration,
                    |                        | standardization,            | aggregation,
                    |                        | normalization,              | business logic and rules
                    |                        | derive columns,             |
                    |                        | enrichement                 |
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Data modeling       | Unmodified             | Unmodified                  | Start schema,
                    |                        |                             | Aggregated objects, Flat tables 
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Target audience     | Data engineers         | Data analysts and engineers | Data analysts, Business users | 
